       → Receive Requests → Accept/Decline
       → Guide Learners → Repeat

💡 Key Design Principles (Mentor Side)
✅ Control
Mentors choose who to accept
✅ Clarity
Requests are detailed
✅ Low Pressure
They can decline without stress
✅ Flexibility
They set limits (availability, mentees)

⚠️ Important Insight (Very Critical)
If mentors feel:
Overwhelmed ❌
Forced ❌
Matched poorly ❌
👉 They will stop using your app
So your system must:
Filter well
Respect their time
Give control

🧠 Smart Features You Can Add Later
Auto-hide mentor when full
“Top mentor” badge
Response rate tracking
Suggested learners (reverse matching 👀)

